                <h2 class="about-title">Professional Summary</h2>

                <p class="about-text border-green">
                  I am a PhD pharmaceutical researcher with a strong academic foundation,
                  holding a Bachelor of Pharmacy followed by an MSc in Pharmaceutics and
                  advanced drug-delivery systems. My research focuses on translating
                  pharmaceutical science into practical, innovative solutions.
                </p>

                <p class="about-text border-yellow">
                  I have authored and co-authored more than a dozen peer-reviewed research
                  publications in advanced drug-delivery systems, 3D bioprinted tumor
                  models, and cancer chemosensitization using novel therapeutic compounds,
                  contributing to precision medicine.
                </p>

                <p class="about-text border-red">
                  In parallel, I am a programmer and full-stack web developer, building
                  research-driven digital platforms that bridge pharmaceutical science
                  with modern web technology.
                </p>

